    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild Cosmos is an introspective game about the self and its relationship with solitude. Play as an astronaut lost in an unknown world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time to be resourceful</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/40e496126d49aabe37de8ddb2439bc8b.poster.avif?t=1762427934\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/40e496126d49aabe37de8ddb2439bc8b.webm?t=1762427934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/40e496126d49aabe37de8ddb2439bc8b.mp4?t=1762427934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up shortly after crashing into an unknown asteroid belt. Your ship may have broken down, your strength may not be your strong point, but you're resourceful and tenacious. Explore this alien world, leap between asteroids and find a way to repair your spaceship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No up and down</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/0b5d250ef8786ddd053c0acb25e839a0.poster.avif?t=1762427934\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/0b5d250ef8786ddd053c0acb25e839a0.webm?t=1762427934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/0b5d250ef8786ddd053c0acb25e839a0.mp4?t=1762427934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The asteroid belt is an entirely 3D world to explore. Secrets may lurk in every nook and cranny. Use your keen eye to find moons and other asteroids on the way to other planets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore and find your own way</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/c459868ba4d7de8f2d821ac5463d84b4.poster.avif?t=1762427934\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/c459868ba4d7de8f2d821ac5463d84b4.webm?t=1762427934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/c459868ba4d7de8f2d821ac5463d84b4.mp4?t=1762427934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why did you decide to travel into space? This infinite, cold, empty place. How far will you go, little astronaut?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An uncharted world</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/4bec9ff9c96a157dc0e6f922afc9552a.poster.avif?t=1762427934\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/4bec9ff9c96a157dc0e6f922afc9552a.webm?t=1762427934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051070/extras/4bec9ff9c96a157dc0e6f922afc9552a.mp4?t=1762427934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't know much about this place. Beware of the flora and fauna of the asteroid belt, where untamed animals live. Some are friendly, others less so. Use your wits and good judgment to navigate this unfamiliar world.</p>",
